00:00:37.960 --> 00:00:40.760
That means there's a huge demand for
mobile programmers.

00:00:40.760 --> 00:00:44.450
Specifically iOS programmers and
Android programmers.

00:00:44.450 --> 00:00:47.250
What's different about mobile
programmers is that they work closely

00:00:47.250 --> 00:00:49.870
with the actual hardware
of mobile phones.

